OL,3,CBroken ticket machine dispute could
OL,4,Clead to 75,000 cases being overturned
OL,6,FA rail passenger who challenged a fine
OL,7,Fafter she was unable to buy a train
OL,8,Fticket has become a test case in a
OL,9,Flegal battle which could see 75,000
OL,10,Fothers overturned.
OL,12,FSarah Cook, who runs a pet shop in
OL,13,FBarnsley, got on a train at Wombwell
OL,14,Fstation in South Yorkshire without
OL,15,Fpaying the #4 fare because the ticket
OL,16,Fmachine was broken.
OL,18,FShe later appealed a #20 fine, but was
OL,19,Ftold she could be convicted and face a
OL,20,F#500 fine under a system called the
OL,21,Fsingle justice procedure (SJP).
