OL,6,FBefore taking her to court, Northern
OL,7,FRail agreed to drop the case as long
OL,8,Fas she paid the original fare from
OL,9,FNovember 2022.
OL,11,FBut Ms Cook was angered by the
OL,12,Fprocess. She said: "If the machines
OL,13,Fand technology don't work, that's a
OL,14,Fflawed system.
OL,16,F"And if your appeal is 'I tried to
OL,17,Fpay, I want to pay', I don't think you
OL,18,Fshould be penalised for that."
