OL,3,CBroken ticket machine dispute could
OL,4,Clead to 75,000 cases being overturned
OL,6,FNow Ms Cook has become one of six
OL,7,Fsimilar "test cases" being looked into
OL,8,Fby the Chief Magistrate at Westminster
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court. Around 75,000
OL,10,Fcases are believed to be involved.
OL,12,FMs Cook said when she received a
OL,13,Fletter informing her of the mass
OL,14,Freview she was in disbelief.
OL,16,F''When I got this I thought it can't
OL,17,Fbe real, why would it be going to
OL,18,FLondon - but now knowing why and
OL,19,Fpotentially that the train company
OL,20,Fwere in the wrong...it's a big deal."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
