OL,4,Clead to 75,000 cases being overturned
OL,6,FSJPs are also used by the DVLA, TV
OL,7,Flicensing, and local authorities over
OL,8,Fschool absences.
OL,10,FIn 2024, the Magistrates' Association,
OL,11,Fwhich represents over 12,000
OL,12,Fmagistrates in England and Wales, has
OL,13,Fcalled for reform of the system.
OL,15,FMark Beattie JP, National Chair of the
OL,16,FMagistrates' Association, said there
OL,17,Fare concerns about the way it operates
OL,18,Fand the harm that it can cause some of
OL,19,Fthe most vulnerable in society, who
OL,20,Fmay not understand the process.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
