OL,6,FHe said: ''We also think there should
OL,7,Fbe more transparency. We would welcome
OL,8,Fa situation where accredited
OL,9,Fjournalists could listen in to SJP
OL,10,Fsessions - in the same way they can
OL,11,Fwalk into any court room in England
OL,12,Fand Wales.''
OL,14,FTravel expert Simon Calder said the
OL,15,Fcurrent system doesn't catch the right
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,18,F''Using the SJP and a law dating back
OL,19,Fto the 19th century doens't seem to be
OL,20,Fthe best way to do it," he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
