OL,6,F"Because you catch people who are
OL,7,Ffundmentally innocent and apply large
OL,8,Ffines to them. Hopefully people who
OL,9,Fwere innocent are going to be let
OL,10,Foff.''
OL,12,FNorthern is one of the multiple train
OL,13,Foperators are involved in the review,
OL,14,Fa sopkesperson said: "There are
OL,15,Fmultiple ways to buy a Northern train
OL,16,Fticket including on the app, our
OL,17,Fwebsite, from ticket vending machines
OL,18,For ticket offices - and our colleagues
OL,19,Fare happy to provide advice if needed.
