OL,6,F"We remind people of the need to buy
OL,7,Ftickets at stations and on trains.
OL,9,F"Our focus remains on ensuring that
OL,10,Fall our customers are treated fairly,
OL,11,Fwhich means ensuring all passengers
OL,12,Fwho board our trains have a valid
OL,13,Fticket. Northern stopped bringing new
OL,14,Fcases under the Single Justice
OL,15,FProcedure for offences under the
OL,16,FRegulation of Railways Act 1889 in
OL,17,FJanuary and are reviewing its previous
OL,18,Fuse."
